    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E92 BMW M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart is the S65 4.0L V8, featuring eight individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system, delivering a visceral 8,400 RPM redline. This example features the preferred 6-speed longitudinal manual gearbox and a carbon fiber reinforced plastic (CFRP) roof for a lower center of gravity. The chassis dynamics are sharpened by a variable M Differential Lock and Electronic Damper Control (EDC). Significant preventative maintenance has been performed, including rod bearing replacement with treated shells and upgraded throttle actuators, ensuring the valvetrain and bottom end are track-ready. The hydraulic steering rack remains precise, offering the tactile feedback modern electric systems lack. A driver-focused machine in solid mechanical health.",
